<br>
With the madness controlling her, Mika leaned down and began to kiss Nefi.  She was trying to suck her warmth, turn nefi into a cold thing like her; but Nefi was too strong for that.  <br>
<br>
Color returned to Mika's face, the frost disapeared.  Mika's eyes returned to their normal color and the madness temporarily left her.  Nefi had not been affected.  <br>
<br>
Mika pulled away and crumpled on the floor next to her friend.  She was exahusted.  Nefi rolled over and looked at her.  <br>
&quot;are you ok?&quot; she asked.  &quot;yes.  I feel fine.  i don't know how long i can keep my sanity intact.  we must find and destroy the cause of my transformations, before i'm lost forever.&quot;<br>
<br>
Mika stared into Nefi's eyes and then realized what had happened.  Nefi had used her own energy to help bring Mika back.  Mika stared, a tear forming in her eye.  Their lips met and Mika knew she was in love. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub95.ezboard.com/umegrua.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Megrua</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/white_fire.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 10<br> <font color=#FF0000>(9/6/02 7:56 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub95.ezboard.com/ffantasystoriesforumfrm7.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=6.topic&index=205>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Me n' Devin goin a huntin'</span><hr size=1> Carmen just sat in the kitchen, thi swas all so weird. She'd just stay here for now. If they needed her, they just had to give a shout. As she lay her head on the table top, her hair sprawled about her head in pale gold wisps. <p><HTML>
