to the door.  One peered out to see what was happening, but he didn't quite get to see as a pair of fists slammed down onto the nape of his neck. The other turned to see as he fired a random shot.  Devin delivered a quick kick to the neck and it was out cold.  A bullet whizzed past Jerron's face as the third brute saw what was transpiring.  &quot;Let's go!&quot;  Devin put his hand on Jerron's shoulder as he leant down to touch the two unconscious brutes.  The four dissapeared from sight as another bullet flew right through were Jerron had been mere seconds before.  Jerron and Devin appeared with the two unconscious men, alone in Derek's appartment.  &quot;Whats goin on Dev?&quot;  Is Lor ok?!  Is Mika?, did they take them to the hospital, was it too late for her, either her.  I love them both, in very different ways.  Derek will know what to do, he always does.  Jerron raised his cellcom to his ear as he spoke Derek's name and got a dial-tone.<br>
