Derek turned sharply, and headed down with the flow of gravity to avoid a head-on collision. Gasping for breath, Mika asked, &quot;Why the hell are we going to Peru?&quot;<br>
<br>
He turned his arm around to put his hand on Mika's throat. She pulled away, as if thinking it a threat, and nearly clocked him. Absent mindedly, he moved his head to the side, and said, &quot;Because I don't want you goin all Lumina on us. You belong with the world of the living, Mika.&quot;<br>
