<br>
Mika huffed. &quot;Whatever. What does this have to do with Peru?&quot;<br>
<br>
Derek slid into a parking spot next to a transport tube. The tube went straight to the lobby; hopefully, there would be, like, ten seats left on the plane for them all. &quot;I got a hunch she's in Peru.&quot;<br>
<br>
Wide eyes stared at him. &quot;A hunch?&quot; they all seemed to say.<br>
<br>
Derek's eyes were wide. When he realize just how foolish this all sounded, he braced for impact... &quot;So... do you wanna just go home? Wait out the Lamia deal, possibley lose Mika?&quot; Derek's mind was made up. He was going, regardless... <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub95.ezboard.com/umegrua.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Megrua</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/white_fire.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 11<br> <font color=#FF0000>(9/15/02 6:33 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub95.ezboard.com/ffantasystoriesforumfrm7.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=6.topic&index=210>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Covert 'perations</span><hr size=1> ** Is Carmen with your all or no she still in the kitchen?** <p><HTML>
